Oncology Products & Prescribing Information










Cancer is one of the world's most urgent unmet medical needs.
Helping people fight cancer is our passion. We are committed to developing breakthrough biomedical innovations to help extend and improve the lives of people with cancer worldwide.



EMEND®  

(aprepitant) capsules (aprepitant) for oral suspension
Prescribing Information
Patient Product Information
Instructions for Use
Product website 


EMEND®
(fosaprepitant dimeglumine) for injection, for intravenous use
Prescribing Information (5.4 mg EDTA formulation)
Prescribing Information (18.8 mg EDTA formulation)
Patient Product Information








