Merck & Co. - Wikipedia






















 






Merck & Co.

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

Not to be confused with the Merck Group (Merck KGaA), its original parent company which owns the rights to the name "Merck" in 191 of 193 countries.

Merck & Co., Inc.






